<th class="navbox-group" style="">1926-1950</th>
<td class="navbox-list navbox-even" style=""><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r151529978"/><span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Grazia_Deledda" title="Grazia Deledda">Deledda</a> (1926)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Henri_Bergson" title="Henri Bergson">Bergson</a> (1927)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Sigrid_Undset" title="Sigrid Undset">Undset</a> (1928)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Thomas_Mann" title="Thomas Mann">Mann</a> (1929)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Sinclair_Lewis" title="Sinclair Lewis">Lewis</a> (1930)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Erik_Axel_Karlfeldt" title="Erik Axel Karlfeldt">Karlfeldt</a> (1931)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/John_Galsworthy" title="John Galsworthy">Galsworthy</a> (1932)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Ivan_Bounine" title="Ivan Bounine">Bounine</a> (1933)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Luigi_Pirandello" title="Luigi Pirandello">Pirandello</a> (1934)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><small><i>non décerné</i></small> (1935)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Eugene_O%27Neill" title="Eugene O&#39;Neill">O'Neill</a> (1936)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Roger_Martin_du_Gard" title="Roger Martin du Gard">Martin du Gard</a> (1937)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Pearl_Buck" title="Pearl Buck">Buck</a> (1938)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Frans_Emil_Sillanp%C3%A4%C3%A4" title="Fran