<th class="navbox-group" style="">2001-aujourd'hui</th>
<td class="navbox-list navbox-even" style=""><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r151529978"/><span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Doris_Lessing" title="Doris Lessing">Doris Lessing</a> (2001)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Arthur_Miller" title="Arthur Miller">Arthur Miller</a> (2002)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Fatima_Mernissi" title="Fatima Mernissi">Fatima Mernissi</a> et <a href="/wiki/Susan_Sontag" title="Susan Sontag">Susan Sontag</a> (2003)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Claudio_Magris" title="Claudio Magris">Claudio Magris</a> (2004)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/N%C3%A9lida_Pi%C3%B1%C3%B3n" title="Nélida Piñón">Nélida Piñón</a> (2005)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Paul_Auster" title="Paul Auster">Paul Auster</a> (2006)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Amos_Oz" title="Amos Oz">Amos Oz</a> (2007)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Margaret_Atwood" title="Margaret Atwood">Margaret Atwood</a> (2008)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Isma%C3%AFl_Kadar%C3%A9" title="Ismaïl Kadaré">Ismaïl Kadaré</a> (2009)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Amin_Maalouf" title="Amin Maalouf">Amin Maalouf</a> (2010)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Leonard_Cohen" title="Leonard Cohen">Leonard Cohen</a> (2011)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Philip_Roth" title="Philip Roth">Philip Roth</a> (2012)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Antonio_Mu%C3%B1oz_Molina" title="Antonio Muño